cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.CYBER, cs.DB 

The paper involves the use of machine learning techniques on big data platform to predict customer churn in the telecom industry. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also uses Social Network Analysis (SNA) features, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.SOC (Social and Societal Aspects of Technology). Additionally, the paper deals with data management and processing, which could place it in cs.DB (Databases). Finally, since the paper deals with customer churn prediction, it could also belong to cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy).
